snippet.title: Johnny Depp Sues ACLU Regarding Claims About Amber Heard Donating Divorce Settlement Money
snippet.description:
In his lawsuit, the 57-year-old actor 'respectfully requests that this Court enter an order directing the ACLU Witnesses to fully comply with the Subpoenas' to verify whether his ex donated the money.  May 20, 2021   AceShowbiz - Johnny Depp has made another move to prove that his ex Amber Heard lied in court about donating her divorce settlement money to the ACLU and Children's Hospital Los Angeles.
